concern on applying this error correction coding to DS8-PSK

modulation scheme) will be either mapped to 1 out of 3 cases

in the column corresponding to that symbol. By using this

encoding method, we indirectly increase the Hamming

distance between two adjacent symbols in the constellation

diagram and somehow spreading the distance equally among

symbols. The Hamming distance between two groups in Table

1 could be calculated using the following equation:

