minimum Hamming distance among symbols to 3. This is the

main factor make our proposed coding technique be efficient

in lowering the symbol error rate significantly.

B. AIEC Decoder
AIEC decoder core principle based on a fully-connect multilayer perceptron neural network. The sample set of parameters (number of hidden layers, number of neurons, an optimizing algorithm, etc.) we used for designing the AIEC decoder is provided in Table 2.

Table 2. A sample of parameters set for designing an AIEC decoder

