IV. EXPERIMENTAL RESULTS To prove the enhancement of our proposed error correction scheme on the communication reliability, we set up the experiment for analyzing the symbol error rate of DS8-PSK receiver side while using our AIEC coding technique, and compare it with the non-FEC Rx. The datasets for SER evaluation is prepared by using LabVIEW, with 106 encoded noisy symbols for each signal to noise ratio (SNR) value. Figure 6 shows our experiment result over additive Gaussian white noise (AWGN) channel.
